title: Schoenberg, Berg, Webern - Orchestral Music - Karajan, BPO
description:
Schoenberg, Berg, Webern: Orchestral Music.

The orchestral music of Arnold Schoenberg, Alban Berg, and Anton Webern, recorded by Herbert von Karajan and the Berlin Philharmonic Orchestra in 1973/4 and released by DG as a three CD set in 1997.

The music performed is as follows:

Disc 1

Schoenberg: Pelleas und Melisande op. 5, Variations for Orchestra op 31

Disc 2

Schoenberg: Verklarte Nacht op. 4
Berg: 3 Pieces for Orchestra op. 6, 3 Pieces from the "Lyric Suite"

Disc 3

Webern: Passacaglia op. 1, 5 Movements op. 5, 6 Pieces for Orchestra op. 6, Symphony op. 21

Please enjoy.
